s of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/47759/', '', 'Amisulpride, Brexpiprazole, Pimavanserin', 'Amisulpride, Loxapine, Pimavanserin', 1767369485);
